00:43:08.702 --> 00:43:10.704 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’re determined ‘to consult that Law

00:43:10.704 --> 00:43:13.974 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so that we can practice it
and then teach it.’

00:43:13.974 --> 00:43:16.443 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And in view
of all the potential distractions,

00:43:16.443 --> 00:43:20.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
let’s make it our aim to use
our eyes, our mind, and our heart

00:43:20.781 --> 00:43:25.786 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to focus attention on the goodness
of Jehovah’s spiritual provisions.

