00:46:52.793 --> 00:46:54.795 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is a goal for many.

00:46:54.795 --> 00:46:58.432 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Recently, thousands of brothers and sisters

00:46:58.432 --> 00:47:01.068 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
sacrificed their time and energy

00:47:01.068 --> 00:47:05.572 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to build a beautiful new
branch facility in Britain.

00:47:05.572 --> 00:47:08.909 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Would you like to see
the results of their hard work

00:47:08.909 --> 00:47:11.411 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the blessings they received?

00:47:11.411 --> 00:47:13.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Please enjoy this report.

00:47:15.816 --> 00:47:19.887 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How will you feel
when all we came here to do

00:47:19.887 --> 00:47:22.523 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is finally completed?

00:47:22.523 --> 00:47:24.691 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No doubt, we will find a moment to reflect

00:47:24.691 --> 00:47:28.228 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on the words of Philippians 2:13.

00:47:28.228 --> 00:47:31.398 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, Jehovah energized us

00:47:31.398 --> 00:47:34.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and gave each and every one of us
“both the desire

00:47:34.201 --> 00:47:37.271 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the power to act.”

00:47:37.271 --> 00:47:41.909 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How has sharing on this project
affected your life?

00:47:42.576 --> 00:47:45.679 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It all started over seven years ago.

00:48:00.894 --> 00:48:04.364 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Can you imagine how excited
you’re going to be

00:48:04.364 --> 00:48:08.035 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when we hear
that the new branch facility at Chelmsford

00:48:08.035 --> 00:48:10.971 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has been approved by the City Council?

00:48:10.971 --> 00:48:12.205 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, guess what?

00:48:12.205 --> 00:48:16.243 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yesterday afternoon we received the approval.

00:50:45.459 --> 00:50:48.295 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Whilst the buildings are beautiful,

00:50:48.295 --> 00:50:51.732 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at the end of the day,
they are just buildings.

00:50:51.732 --> 00:50:53.867 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The really special part of this project

00:50:53.867 --> 00:50:55.969 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has been the people;

00:50:56.870 --> 00:51:00.240 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even non-Witnesses saw that something special

00:51:00.240 --> 00:51:02.642 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was taking place on our site.

00:51:02.642 --> 00:51:04.878 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s a very friendly site to work on.

00:51:04.878 --> 00:51:06.880 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s just how friendly everyone is.

00:51:06.880 --> 00:51:10.317 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You walk in, and it just—
I find it mind-blowing.

00:51:10.317 --> 00:51:12.252 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In a negative (sometimes) society,

00:51:12.252 --> 00:51:15.388 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when you come here,
it just puts a smile on your face.

00:51:15.388 --> 00:51:18.091 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A truly unexpected success

00:51:18.091 --> 00:51:20.393 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was the visitors’ center.

00:51:20.393 --> 00:51:22.763 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How we underestimated the appreciation

00:51:22.763 --> 00:51:25.098 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s people have

00:51:25.098 --> 00:51:27.167 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for theocratic activities.

00:51:27.167 --> 00:51:30.504 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Visitors from all around the globe witnessed

00:51:30.504 --> 00:51:32.873 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the activities of Jehovah for themselves.

00:51:33.940 --> 00:51:35.942 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is partly why

00:51:35.942 --> 00:51:39.513 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m actually studying the Bible
to get baptized,

00:51:39.513 --> 00:51:42.649 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because when I came here,
it just hit me somewhere, you know?

00:51:44.684 --> 00:51:47.554 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Me and Alicia can’t see,

00:51:47.554 --> 00:51:50.190 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so everyone has been
so encouraging and thoughtful.

00:51:50.190 --> 00:51:54.361 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We really feel like Jehovah is with us
and he’s supported us.

00:51:55.295 --> 00:51:59.299 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I really liked the ladies driving tractors.

00:52:01.768 --> 00:52:04.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Everyone wanted to have
a part in the project.

00:52:05.038 --> 00:52:07.808 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Every single contribution warmed our hearts

00:52:08.375 --> 00:52:11.311 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and sometimes our heads too.

00:52:12.479 --> 00:52:15.348 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Another beautiful project highlight

00:52:15.348 --> 00:52:17.350 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was the day-volunteer program.

00:52:17.350 --> 00:52:20.453 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The effort and expense brothers and sisters

00:52:20.453 --> 00:52:22.923 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
sacrificed reminded all of us

00:52:22.923 --> 00:52:26.626 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of what a privilege it is
to work for Jehovah.

00:52:26.626 --> 00:52:29.763 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And how about the commuters
who helped on the project?

00:52:29.763 --> 00:52:32.165 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Would the BRD family have had

00:52:32.165 --> 00:52:34.501 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the same spirit without our commuters?

00:52:37.170 --> 00:52:41.441 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Don’t you just love being a part
of this amazing family?

00:52:45.178 --> 00:52:48.615 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We were regularly reminded that spirituality

00:52:48.615 --> 00:52:50.450 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is of the utmost importance.

00:52:51.651 --> 00:52:53.653 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Did you ever say that a monthly meeting

00:52:53.653 --> 00:52:55.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was the best one yet?

00:52:56.523 --> 00:53:00.360 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What lies outside the comfort zone

00:53:00.360 --> 00:53:02.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is the faith zone.

00:53:02.562 --> 00:53:04.998 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Don’t cry because it’s over;

00:53:04.998 --> 00:53:07.300 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
smile because it happened.

00:53:08.969 --> 00:53:12.339 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What is your story?

00:53:12.339 --> 00:53:15.542 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The center of all of our stories is Jehovah.

00:53:15.542 --> 00:53:18.345 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He is the one who energized us;

00:53:18.345 --> 00:53:21.047 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
he is the one who gave us
both the desire

00:53:21.047 --> 00:53:23.416 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the power to act.

00:53:23.416 --> 00:53:25.619 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He is the one we can thank

00:53:25.619 --> 00:53:27.587 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for the lifelong friendships we have formed,

00:53:27.587 --> 00:53:29.389 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the training we have received,

00:53:29.389 --> 00:53:32.993 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the challenges
we have been able to overcome.

00:53:32.993 --> 00:53:35.962 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Remember your story.

00:53:35.962 --> 00:53:39.799 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Really, it’s only just beginning.

00:53:48.441 --> 00:53:50.510 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In this month’s program,

00:53:50.510 --> 00:53:54.881 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we learned what it means
to pay attention to Jehovah.

00:53:54.881 --> 00:53:58.685 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We saw how we can stay focused on Jehovah

00:53:58.685 --> 00:54:02.355 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
despite potential distractions.

00:54:02.355 --> 00:54:05.292 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Elders are good shepherds

00:54:05.292 --> 00:54:07.827 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because they are attentive
to Jehovah’s instruction.

00:54:10.630 --> 00:54:13.767 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our ministry is more effective

00:54:13.767 --> 00:54:17.237 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when we focus
on reaching the hearts of people.

00:54:18.204 --> 00:54:19.739 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And our new song

00:54:19.739 --> 00:54:23.643 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
reminds our young adults
to keep their eyes

00:54:23.643 --> 00:54:27.147 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on the prize of life.

00:54:27.147 --> 00:54:29.549 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Before we say goodbye,

00:54:29.549 --> 00:54:32.385 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
let’s go to the southwest tip of Japan

00:54:32.385 --> 00:54:36.890 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and visit our brothers and sisters
in the Ishigaki Congregation.

00:54:38.591 --> 00:54:41.428 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Their territory includes the Yaeyama Islands,

00:54:41.428 --> 00:54:43.430 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
an archipelago

00:54:43.430 --> 00:54:47.834 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of 12 islands
and more than 360 coral reefs.

00:54:47.834 --> 00:54:51.638 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Emerald-green waters
surround these lush,

00:54:51.638 --> 00:54:53.640 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
jungle-covered islands.

00:54:53.640 --> 00:54:55.842 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With almost no light pollution,

00:54:55.842 --> 00:54:59.212 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this is an ideal place to observe

00:54:59.212 --> 00:55:01.848 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s beautiful heavenly creation.

00:55:03.483 --> 00:55:08.388 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Vast distances between the islands
make the ministry a challenge.

00:55:08.388 --> 00:55:11.057 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To reach remote communities,

00:55:11.057 --> 00:55:15.061 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
publishers take ferries and small airplanes.

00:55:15.061 --> 00:55:19.332 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is costly,
and economic conditions here aren’t easy.

00:55:20.500 --> 00:55:24.337 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Transportation includes bicycles

00:55:24.337 --> 00:55:27.207 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as well as carts and wagons
pulled by water buffalo.

00:55:29.209 --> 00:55:31.277 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Public witnessing is an effective way

00:55:31.277 --> 00:55:33.513 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to share the good news

00:55:33.513 --> 00:55:35.515 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with the many tourists who travel here.

00:55:35.515 --> 00:55:37.550 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
More than one million

00:55:37.550 --> 00:55:41.121 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
visited during one recent year.

00:55:41.121 --> 00:55:43.923 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Contact cards also produce good results.

00:55:45.125 --> 00:55:49.396 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Ishigaki Congregation has 112 publishers,

00:55:49.396 --> 00:55:53.400 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
including 35 regular pioneers.

00:55:53.400 --> 00:55:57.737 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They’re conducting
more than 100 Bible studies every month.

00:55:59.472 --> 00:56:03.510 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Kingdom Hall
is in Ishigaki City on the main island.

00:56:03.510 --> 00:56:05.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Talks from this Kingdom Hall

00:56:05.812 --> 00:56:08.648 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are streamed to this small meeting place

00:56:08.648 --> 00:56:10.784 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for the seven brothers and sisters

00:56:10.784 --> 00:56:13.720 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who live on remote Iriomote Island.

00:56:15.755 --> 00:56:19.392 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The publishers work together
to maintain the Kingdom Hall,

00:56:20.960 --> 00:56:23.530 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and they enjoy upbuilding association

00:56:23.530 --> 00:56:26.499 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in this beautiful land.

00:56:26.499 --> 00:56:30.370 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our brothers and sisters
in the Ishigaki Congregation

00:56:30.370 --> 00:56:32.405 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
send their warm love and greetings.

00:56:32.405 --> 00:56:34.307 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
From the World Headquarters

00:56:34.307 --> 00:56:36.309 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:56:36.309 --> 00:56:39.746 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this is JW Broadcasting.

